  <brief_title>Study of Surgically-Induced Weight Loss on Pelvic Floor Disorders</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Cohort Study of the Impact of Surgically-Induced Weight Loss on Pelvic Floor Disorders</official_title>
  <sponsors>
